                <note rend="inline" type="source">838.51/1128: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Haiti</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bailly-Blanchard</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-08-17T16:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 17, 1921—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>49. Your 56, August 10, 4 p.m.</p>
                <p>Payments to President and officials named to have precedence over Sanitation and
                    Public Works but not over Constabulary. Settlement outlined approved.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
